OL,3,CInvestigation launched into potential
OL,4,Cexploitation in university loans system
OL,6,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,7,Fhas asked counter-fraud experts to
OL,8,Flead an investigation into the
OL,9,Funiversity loans system over fears
OL,10,Fstudents are claiming millions of
OL,11,Fpounds with no intent to study.
OL,13,FMs Phillipson directed the Public
OL,14,FSector Fraud Authority to help co-
OL,15,Fordinate the response to the
OL,16,Fallegations and support the
OL,17,Finvestigations already under way.
