OL,3,CInvestigation launched into potential
OL,4,Cexploitation in university loans system
OL,6,FIt follows a Sunday Times
OL,7,Finvestigation, which reports thousands
OL,8,Fof students with "no academic intent"
OL,9,Fare suspected of fraudulently claiming
OL,10,Fhundreds of millions of pounds from
OL,11,Fthe country's university loans system.
OL,13,FThe newspaper said most of the
OL,14,Fstudents under scrutiny are thought to
OL,15,Fbe at "franchised" universities, which
OL,16,Fare colleges paid to provide courses
OL,17,Ffor established universities.
