OL,3,CInvestigation launched into potential
OL,4,Cexploitation in university loans system
OL,6,FThere is a concern of potential
OL,7,F"organised recruitment" of Romanian
OL,8,Fnationals in particular to enrol on
OL,9,Fcourses, according to the Sunday Times.
OL,11,FIt said the Student Loans Company
OL,12,F(SLC) spotted suspicious applications
OL,13,Finvolving fake documents and address
OL,14,Fduplication, and franchised colleges
OL,15,Fare enrolling students who cannot
OL,16,Fspeak adequate English.
