OL,3,CInvestigation launched into potential
OL,4,Cexploitation in university loans system
OL,6,FWriting for the newspaper, Ms
OL,7,FPhillipson said: "Today's revelations
OL,8,Fof major misuse of public money and
OL,9,Fpotential fraud by students in
OL,10,Ffranchised universities deal a hammer
OL,11,Fblow to the integrity of higher
OL,12,Feducation in this country.
OL,14,F"They point to one of the biggest
OL,15,Ffinancial scandals in the history of
OL,16,Four universities sector. They demand
OL,17,Fthe firmest action."
