OL,3,CInvestigation launched into potential
OL,4,Cexploitation in university loans system
OL,6,FShe added that franchising in some
OL,7,Finstitutions has "become less about
OL,8,Fexpanding access and more about
OL,9,Fmeeting expanding overheads for hard-
OL,10,Fup universities", and said the system
OL,11,Falso "lacks necessary guardrails
OL,12,Fagainst abuse".
OL,14,FMs Phillipson said the Office for
OL,15,FStudents (OfS) "should have provided
OL,16,Fthese guardrails", adding that she has
OL,17,Fasked the Public Sector Fraud
OL,18,FAuthority to "co-ordinate immediate
OL,19,Faction across the system to halt this
OL,20,Fgrowing threat".
