OL,4,Cexploitation in university loans system
OL,6,FThe education secretary added: "The
OL,7,FStudent Loans Company has been working
OL,8,Fwith law-enforcement agencies to
OL,9,Finvestigate the prevalence of some
OL,10,FRomanian students at certain
OL,11,Finstitutions, but not enough care was
OL,12,Ftaken to join the dots of wider abuse
OL,13,Ftaking place across the system and to
OL,14,Fslam the door shut on widespread abuse.
OL,16,F"But today's revelations demand that
OL,17,Fwe must go further and faster to
OL,18,Fprotect the public purse. I will not
OL,19,Ftolerate a penny of taxpayers' money
OL,20,Fbeing misused."
