OL,3,CInvestigation launched into potential
OL,4,Cexploitation in university loans system
OL,6,F"Our plan for change will restore
OL,7,Ftrust in our universities. We have
OL,8,Falready taken clear action to crack
OL,9,Fdown on rogue franchise operators to
OL,10,Ftackle fraud and we'll go further. We
OL,11,Fwill overhaul regulation so the Office
OL,12,Ffor Students (OfS) better-protects
OL,13,Ftaxpayers' money. In the meantime, we
OL,14,Fhave asked the OfS to clamp down on
OL,15,Ffranchising.
