OL,6,F"The Education Secretary has asked the
OL,7,FPublic Sector Fraud Authority to help
OL,8,Fco-ordinate the cross-government
OL,9,Fresponse to these extremely concerning
OL,10,Fallegations and support the
OL,11,Finvestigations already under way.
OL,13,F"Where misuse or fraud is found we
OL,14,Fhave powers to claw back payments `
OL,15,Fand we won't hesitate to use them. We
OL,16,Fwill bring in tough new laws to ensure
OL,17,Fthe OfS can quickly stop bad actors
OL,18,Fgaming the system once and for all."
