OL,6,FThe Student Loans Company has blocked
OL,7,Fstudent finance payments after similar
OL,8,Fconcerns were previously identified,
OL,9,Fit is understood.
OL,11,FOfS chief executive Susan Lapworth
OL,12,Fsaid: "The public must have confidence
OL,13,Fthat taxpayers' money in the form of
OL,14,Fstudent loans is well spent ` with
OL,15,Fgenuine students attending high-
OL,16,Fquality courses that lead to good
OL,17,Foutcomes.
